### ML Models API Tests
### Use with VS Code REST Client extension

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000/api/v1/ml-models

### ============== Health & Status ==============

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Get Model Status
GET {{baseUrl}}/status

### ============== Training ==============

### Train Policy Model
POST {{baseUrl}}/train/policy
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "dataset_path": "/app/data/datasets/v1/game_logs_v1_latest.parquet"
}

### Train Win Probability Model
POST {{baseUrl}}/train/winprob
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "dataset_path": "/app/data/datasets/v1/game_logs_v1_20251215_164025.parquet"
}

### Train Both Models
POST {{baseUrl}}/train/all
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "dataset_path": "/app/data/datasets/v1/game_logs_v1_20251215_164025.parquet"
}

### ============== Load Models ==============

### Load Saved Models
POST {{baseUrl}}/load

